**Problem 2.3â‹† (B)** Show for any orthogonal matrix $Q âˆˆ â„^m$ and
matrix $A âˆˆ â„^{m Ã— n}$ that
$$
\|Q A\|_F = \|A\|_F
$$
by first showing that $\|A \|_F = \sqrt{\hbox{tr}(A^âŠ¤ A)}$ using the
_trace_ of an $m Ã— m$ matrix:
$$
